    <description>L-shaped corridor (4 m wide) with a 13 m horizontal leg and a 5.5 m vertical leg, sized for a TurtleBot3 waffle. Four small wall-mounted desks (0.8 x 0.5 x 0.75 m) distributed along both legs as static obstacles.</description>
